OL,4,Cannounced
OL,6,FThe four-day event will be held at the
OL,7,FHarmony Gardens, in Melrose from 13
OL,8,FJuly 2024.
OL,10,FFestival Director, Alistair Moffat,
OL,11,Fsaid: "It's time to start making plans
OL,12,Ffor those long, light, balmy days at
OL,13,Fthe height of the Scottish summer, and
OL,14,Fwhat better event to pop in the diary
OL,15,Fthan our annual celebration in our
OL,16,Fvery own Borders slice of heaven.
