OL,4,Cannounced
OL,6,F"We sincerely hope that you will all
OL,7,Fbe here, too, as we revel in the joy
OL,8,Fof gathering in high summer to talk
OL,9,Fabout the things we love with the
OL,10,Fpeople we love, before whiling away a
OL,11,Fgentle afternoon or evening surrounded
OL,12,Fby delicious food and drink, enjoying
OL,13,Fthe gorgeous scenery, and absorbing
OL,14,Fthe chitter-chatter of friends and
OL,15,Fother festival goers alike.
OL,17,F"So do come and join us for the
OL,18,Fbiggest party in the Borders!"
